“Alexa,

00:05:18.368 --> 00:05:22.538 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
play the <i>Watchtower </i> study
in Russian from jw.org.”

00:05:22.538 --> 00:05:26.142 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Playing this week’s
<i>Watchtower</i><i> </i> study article in Russian.

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:32.882 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Just remember, though,

00:05:32.882 --> 00:05:35.885 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
