Hello, everyone.

00:06:14.257 --> 00:06:17.093 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’re so happy to have you
with us for this month’s broadcast.

00:06:17.093 --> 00:06:21.964 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
